# Global snippets

snippet (C)
	`&enc[:2] == "utf" ? "Â©" : "(C)"` Copyright `strftime("%Y")` ${1:`g:myFullName`}. All Rights Reserved.${2}
snippet gpl
	Copyright: (C) `strftime('%Y')` ${1:`g:myFullName`}
	  This program is free software; you can redistribute it and/or modify it
	  under the terms of the GNU General Public License.
	  See http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.txt
snippet date
	`strftime("%Y-%m-%d")`
snippet email
	`g:myEmailAddress`
snippet name&email
	`g:myFullName` <${1:`g:myEmailAddress`}>${2}
snippet author
	${2}Author:	`g:myFullName` <${1:`g:myEmailAddress`}>${3}
snippet maintainer
	${2}Maintainer:	`g:myFullName` <${1:`g:myEmailAddress`}>${3}
snippet what
	`WhatString#Generate(exists('b:product') ? b:product : '${1:tools}')`
snippet Re
	Regular expression
snippet Res
	Regular expressions
snippet So
	Stack Overflow
snippet Vim
	Vim version `Version()`
# grawlix, obscenicon, symbol swearing, cp. http://english.stackexchange.com/questions/86838/what-the-is-that-called
snippet fuck
	%&*#
snippet fucking
	%&*#ing
snippet Hex
	Hexadecimal
snippet hex
	hexadecimal
snippet Lorem
	Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit, sed diam nonummy nibh euismod tincidunt ut laoreet dolore magna aliquam erat volutpat.
snippet by
	${1:bit} by $1${2}
snippet by-
	${1:bit}-by-$1${2}
